<li id="cite_note-33"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/celebrating-science/">Celebrating Science Editor in Chief Mariette DiChristina introduces the August 2010 issue of Scientific American</a></span>
